text: Don , of Boldium Architecture has been a pleasure to deal with . He has helped me through the Consent process while seeking to obtain a Consent for my bathroom renovation. I can highly recommend him to those looking to deal with the Auckland City Council  and other works.

I recently worked with Don for my building consent application, and I was very pleased with the service. He were professional, knowledgeable, and efficient, ensuring the process went smoothly. Communication was clear throughout, and he handled all aspects meticulously. I highly recommend his services!

Just wanted to say a sincere thank you Don for all the work you have done for us in creating our amazing new space. We love it and were continually impressed by your professionalism, attention to detail, care and the support you provided us during bathroom, kitchen, wardrobe and wall modifications work. You made the process so easy for us and we are very grateful.
